  "title": "Project Engineer (Electrical)",
  "description": "<ol>\n  <li>Project Engineer (Electrical in Construction related) - 3 to 5 years’ experience with local experience</li>\n  <li>Degree or Diploma in Electrical and Electronics Engineering</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Job Responsibility</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Site  preparation and co-ordination, preparation of submission documents</li>\n  <li>Assist QS to work on tender</li>\n  <li>Coordinate,  liaise and manage various project stakeholders including customers, consultants, sub-contractors, vendors, etc. on site to ensure project requirements are met</li>\n  <li>Able to communicate effectively to all stakeholders</li>\n  <li>Prepare  and create detailed work schedule, manpower and resource planning</li>\n  <li>Able to understand Engineering drawings and perform basic engineering calculations, design, etc.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate the safety management system on site</li>\n  <li>Follow up and report on project progress</li>\n  <li>Able to understand Singapore standards or Code of Practice</li>\n  <li>Other ad-hoc tasks assigned by reporting manager</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently, team player and target oriented in a fast-paced  environment</li>\n  <li>Able to interact effectively with project members and managers at all levels</li>\n</ul>",
